<td><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="000000">Wisdom and Intelligence Effects on Fletching Success</font></td></tr></table></td></tr></table><p><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER" bgcolor="000000">
