<td width="10"><img src="http://www.maximumeq.com/forum/Images/SmallNew.gif" border="0" alt="New Message"></td><td width="50%"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="EEEEEE"><b>RE:Fletching Skills (modified 0 times)</b> </font></td><td width="50%" align="RIGHT"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="EEEEEE"><b>Krys</b></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td><a href="UltraBoard.cgi?Action=ShowProfile&ID=krys&Board=ranger&Idle=30&Sort=0&Order=Descend&Page=0&Session=" target="Profile" OnMouseOver="window.status='View Krys (krys) Profile.';return true;" OnMouseOut="window.status=''"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="000000 ">Profile</font></a></td><td align="RIGHT"></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="EEEEEE">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">OK, some +2int and wis rings will be fairly cheap.  Talk to an enchanter.  Stein of Moggok = 10int for whatever their going for on your server (100p max on Lanys).  Another thing to look into (and this will be easier and cheaper to do) is get some cha gear for buying/selling to vendors.  If you don't pay as much for the materials and sell the product for more, your saving money.  First, get a crude stein (15cha, about 15p or find someone killing ogre guards near oggok).  Split paw necklase is also a cheap 5cha item.  Golden catseye bracers are also fairly cheap and 7cha each.  Also, opaline earrings are 5p each and drop in the estate of unrest.  Carry the cha gear w/ ya, and use it whenever you talk to a merchant (will easily add a pp to each FS weapon you sell).  Don't worry about getting your cha above 140 as it won't affect the prices after that level.  Another thing to improve our prices from merchants that don't like ya too much: get behind them and use the sneak skill.  You'll know you were successful because hte merchant suddenly became indifferent.<p>

Krys</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
